name: FLOWER EARRINGS
description:
Gorgeous resin earrings.

Let these perfect, petite flowers complement any season, outfit or occasion.

Always a sell out.

name: GOLDEN ORIENT BROOCH
description:
Created by immersing Chinese  offering paper in resin this brooch has the most amazing glow. The gold paper almost leaps out at you.

Each brooch is handmade by the girls at Pear Shaped and crafted with love. All of our brooches are unique, and while we endeavour to recreate each style, the unpredictable nature of resin means that slight differences may occur.

name: 'LOST IN NEW YORK'
description:
'Lost in New York' is part of our mapped series. Find your favourite nooks and crannies of the city captured in a resin bangle. Lost in New York? Just show the cabbie your bangle and you'll be home in a jiffy.

Each bangle is handmade by the girls at Pear Shaped and crafted with love. All of our bangles are unique, and while we endeavour to recreate each style, the unpredictable nature of resin means that slight differences may occur.
